Windows 10.0.17134 Version 1803 RTM Spring Creators Update

Windows 10 is your partner in any business. Use the quick launch, familiar, but noticeably improved, the Start menu and new amazing features to work with different devices.

You will also like the advanced features of the new system, for example an entirely new browser for easy Internet browsing.

Spring Creators Update (aka April 2018 Update, also version 1803) is a major update for the Windows 10 operating system, formerly known under the code name Redstone 4
